Package: microeda
Title: Evidence-Guided EDA for Microbiome Count Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("microeda", "authors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "microeda@example.com")
Author: microeda authors [aut, cre]
Maintainer: microeda authors <microeda@example.com>
Description: Provides a lightweight evidence-guided exploratory data
    analysis layer for microbiome count tables. The package inspects count
    tables, sample metadata, and taxonomy, then returns diagnostics and
    method recommendations for compositional, sparse, high-dimensional
    microbiome data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    methods
Suggests:
    phyloseq,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
